---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import FunctionPlotter from '../../../components/diagrams/FunctionPlotter.svelte';
---

<Layout title="Exponential Functions" lang="en" backHref="/explore-math/en/grade-10/" backLabel="← Grade 10">
	<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Exponential Functions</h1>
	<p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8">Describe growth and decay mathematically</p>
	<section class="prose max-w-none">
		<h2>Exponential Growth</h2>
		<p>f(x) = a^x grows faster than any polynomial. Bacteria, interest, radioactive decay.</p>
		<h3>🧪 Experiment</h3>
		<p>Change base a:</p>
	</section>
	<FunctionPlotter client:visible fn={(x, a) => Math.pow(a, x)} fnLabel="y = a^x" showSlider={true} sliderLabel="a" sliderMin={0.5} sliderMax={3} sliderStep={0.1} yMin={-1} yMax={10} />
	<section class="prose max-w-none mt-8">
		<h3>💡 Insights</h3>
		<ul><li>a &gt; 1: exponential growth</li><li>0 &lt; a &lt; 1: exponential decay</li><li>Asymptote at y=0</li><li>Doubling time: t = ln(2)/ln(a)</li></ul>
	</section>
</Layout>
